lead_paragraph: England coach Eddie Jones has said the side's main task in the Autumn internationals will be to take down South Africa's 'bullies' as he aims to build on his successful start in the role with a first win over the Springboks since 2006.

headline.print_headline: Jones Aims to Beat Down Springbok 'Bullies' on Road to 2019
headline.main: Jones Aims to Beat Down Springbok 'Bullies' on Road to 2019
